{"tid":1955311,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疫襲下空運量大減 凍肉供應恐受牽連","createTime":"2020-04-02T11:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T13:37:35.000Z","uid":13468,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3b9c42bdcb91be583a66acaef0603c72af602b8c","tid":1955311,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:29:52.000Z","msg":"疫襲下空運量大減 凍肉供應恐受牽連<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n越南柬埔寨限制白米出口，一度觸發本港糧食搶購潮，聯合國糧農組織更呼籲各國防止新型肺炎疫情引發糧食危機。為剖析本港爆發糧食荒風險，本報訪問糧油商、食物加工廠東主及進口商，發現原來內地早前封城政策一度令罐頭等加工食品未能來港，但隨着內地工廠陸續復工，食品供應已回復正常。米商經歷兩次搶米潮後，目前仍有充足存貨，並因應市民疫情下減少外出，增加家庭裝的「包仔米」供應。至於貴價凍肉則受空運量大減拖累，來港貨量大減，業界長遠擔心，疫情擴散至全球凍肉出口地巴西，將影響未來一個月的凍肉供應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1737954/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1737954%2F&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=0222248d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1737954%2F&h=63bb8bf0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1737954/</a>"},{"pid":"47c09bedb9a3852249c6f8f8fd367d9511821867","tid":1955311,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:42:41.000Z","msg":"食支那肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4b230fa04f31c2bd913bc54a3486bbdb123bf4","tid":1955311,"uid":221265,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:45:34.000Z","msg":"香港人屋企個雪櫃好細<br />\n凍肉冇得搶定<br />\n搶咗雪去邊？"},{"pid":"a7b858709e3d294b89e20e57b25ceb13a4b7cd7a","tid":1955311,"uid":13468,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:55:26.000Z","msg":"劉智穎亦知悉，航班大減令空運來港的凍肉，包括刺身等貴價食品來港貨量大減。不過，隨着疫情近日殺入南美洲，秘魯、智利、哥倫比亞等國陸續鎖國，巴西更成為南美洲最多新型肺炎確診個案的國家。他留意到由上星期開始，往來香港至南美的貨船大減，「由一星期六班減至只有兩班，日後貨運物流可能要用更迂迴的路線，甚至是有貨無船，運不到來香港。」包括巴西在內的南美國家，過去出口大量平價凍肉到港，劉智穎擔心如船運量不足情況持續，一個月後將影響本港凍肉供應。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嚇鬼咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad70e8d5cf32702ca500951d082a65258ec9966","tid":1955311,"uid":211941,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"9e4b230fa04f31c2bd913bc54a3486bbdb123bf4","tid":1955311,"uid":221265,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:45:34.000Z","msg":"香港人屋企個雪櫃好細<br />\n凍肉冇得搶定<br />\n搶咗雪去邊？"},"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:03:40.000Z","msg":"所以下一步係搶雪櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7550aa20c0bd457821de15adad51d97daa696b9","tid":1955311,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cad70e8d5cf32702ca500951d082a65258ec9966","tid":1955311,"uid":211941,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"9e4b230fa04f31c2bd913bc54a3486bbdb123bf4","tid":1955311,"uid":221265,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:45:34.000Z","msg":"香港人屋企個雪櫃好細<br />\n凍肉冇得搶定<br />\n搶咗雪去邊？"},"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:03:40.000Z","msg":"所以下一步係搶雪櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:04:00.000Z","msg":"放邊"},{"pid":"40004ba2a43aa1aad49979ad3c89cbc1a5220063","tid":1955311,"uid":210140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cad70e8d5cf32702ca500951d082a65258ec9966","tid":1955311,"uid":211941,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"9e4b230fa04f31c2bd913bc54a3486bbdb123bf4","tid":1955311,"uid":221265,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:45:34.000Z","msg":"香港人屋企個雪櫃好細<br />\n凍肉冇得搶定<br />\n搶咗雪去邊？"},"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:03:40.000Z","msg":"所以下一步係搶雪櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:04:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\